# compfees

Get protocol fees over time

### Usage

```python wordwrap
/crypto compfees projects
```

---

## Parameters

| Name | Description | Optional | Choices |
| ---- | ----------- | -------- | ------- |
| projects | Comma separated list of protocols (e.g., btc,eth) | False | None |


---

## Examples

```

```

```
/crypto compfees projects: btc,eth
```
